{
  "texts": [
    "However, the model for private school applicant essays achieved lower predictive power with an R 2 value of 0.15.",
    "To emphasize more reliable results, we report findings from public school applicants in this section.",
    "The discrepancy in the models' predictive power could be explained by the following two factors.",
    "First, the private school applicants came from communities with higher levels of EC and lower variation in EC; the lower variation would mean that the model would likely have a harder time distinguishing patterns.",
    "Second, the difference in variation might also be explained by which students are drawn to apply to highly selective universities and the most selective programs in those same schools (engineering)."
  ]
}